".https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/64/Entomologist_chasing_buterflies.jpg[Entomologist chasing butterflies] by Matthieu Gauvain (CC-BY-SA)\n"
"image::data-mobilization::QDataTypes-field.png[align=center,width=640,height=360]\n"
msgstr ":figure-caption!:\n"
".https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/64/Entomologist_chasing_buterflies.jpg[Un entomologiste à la poursuite des papillons] par Matthieu Gauvain (CC-BY-SA)\n"
